story.text: Failed to wake up this morning and work out. Tomorrow is another day. I enjoy the commute so far, but need to work on being comfortable driving well under the speed limit.
Time to set up the home office - need to decide if I will have an office in Nye and Red Lodge, or just the latter. Will need to buy screens, etc for each place.
Excited to see the future of E2. It helps me, I hope it can help others.
